assert_raises_message(errors.CompileException,
    "%def or %block named 'x' already exists in this template", Template,
    """
                <%block>
                <%block name="x">
                    block
                </%block>

                foob

                <%block name="x">
                    block
                </%block>
                </%block>
            """
    )
